Name: Stickman Racer Road Draw 2
About the game: Stickman Racer Road Draw 2 is a legendary survival game where you have to do cool stunts on different vehicles. The game is made in the best traditions of simulators with elements of ragdoll physics. Perform cool jumps and stunts and mercilessly destroy the enemy! Your task is to reach the finish line alive or dead!
